summary: a deku stick, similar to the ones seen in TLOZ ocarina of time
descriptionHtml:
the deku stick model that i created, originally for matt13382 and his zelda mod. this is published as a resource. keep in mind that this is my first completed model, and i strongly encourage users to modify or enhance the model, however any modifications intended for sharing MUST be reuploaded to my page for users to download. credit will be given.

enjoy!

model details:
model is unscaled and untextured, 16,535 triangles, saved as a .obj
author: greg079
